Barn: Gunnar f. 14, riksbanks-tj :man, Lars 19, gymn :dir. — Stud:ex. 031 An’st. i rüksbaniken 03-17, ensk. banik 17-22’, stadsrev. i Norriköp. 23-26 o. stadskamr. där sed. 26. Ordf. i styr. f. riksb. avd :kont. i Norrköp. sed. 36. RVOIM.
translated: Höglund, Sven Viktor Os;sian, city accountant, Norrköping, b. May 30, 1885 in Mariestad to bank clerk Ossian H. and Hildur Bäckström. Married to Ingrid Lundblad. Children: Gunnar b. 1914, official at the National Bank, Lars b. 1909, gymnasium director. Passed his studentexamen from the Anstalten in 1903 and worked at the National Bank 1917-1922. Became city auditor in Norrköping from 1923-1926 and city accountant from 1926. He has been chairman of the board for the National Bank's office in Norrköping since 1936. Awarded RVOIM.
